items.name: Pet Food Kibble
items.description: A simple, preserved type of kibble. Not an effective taming food, but an excellent, easy-to-make pet food to fill your troughs. Almost anything will eat it.

items.name: Alpha Blood
items.description: Blood from an Additional Alpha. Its genetic makeup is very strange, but it has some practical purposes, regardless of the non-viable material therin.

items.name: .S.P.E.K.T.O.R. Genome Assembly
items.description: A modified stasis chamber used to manufacture genetic life.

items.name: .S.P.E.K.T.O.R. Genetics Table
items.description: Looks a little rusted, but the equipment should still be able to perform the genetic experiments needed.

items.name: Huntsman's Boomerang
items.description: Straight from the outback of ARKstralia, this isnt the typical toy you're used to. One good throw from this aboriginal weapon, if it doesnt kill, will knock any small-to-mid sized creature on it's rear or leave it winded.

items.name: Wooden Spear Bolt
items.description: A spear that has been shortened, able to be fired from a bow. It deals great damage.  If it doesn't break, you can recover your ammo.

items.name: Mothball Grenade
items.description: Pulling the pin starts a 5 second timer to an explosion.  Make sure you've thrown it by then. Causes no damage, but effects similar to Lymantria spores. Useful for speeding up passive tames.

items.name: Muhreetle
items.description: Used by primitive tribes, this spiked club has extremely short range but is absolutely brutal, thanks to the keratinous spines adorning it; which also allow it to penetrate armor & bleed out its victims. Rated 10/10 Ooga for your Booga by brawlers

items.name: Prime Dart
items.description: A shock dart, increased in potency with the strange Alpha Blood material found in Additional Alphas. Never spoils, easier to carry, 3x potency of shock darts

items.name: Improved Tranq Dart
items.description: A potent dart for when you can't wait for Shock Darts. Between normal and Shocking in potency. Roughly 1/2 times stronger than normal darts!
